    "id": "nce2-001-a-private-conversation",
    "title": "Lesson 1: A Private Conversation",
    "audioFilename": "01－A Private Conversation.mp3",
    "duration": 78.55,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.21,
      "end": 1.51,
      "text": "Lesson 1.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第1课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 2.05,
      "end": 3.57,
      "text": "A Private Conversation.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "私人谈话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 5.27,
      "end": 8.53,
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 9.83,
      "end": 13.95,
      "text": "Why did the writer complain to the people behind him?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "作者为什么向坐在他身后的人抱怨？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 16.02,
      "end": 18.54,
      "text": "Last week I went to the theater.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "上星期我去看戏。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 19.3,
      "end": 21.28,
      "text": "I had a very good seat.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我的座位很好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 22.06,
      "end": 24.1,
      "text": "The play was very interesting.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那出戏很有意思。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 25.02,
      "end": 26.76,
      "text": "I did not enjoy it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "但我却无法欣赏。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 27.24,
      "end": 31.3,
      "text": "A young man and a young woman were sitting behind me.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "一青年男子和一青年女子坐在我的身后。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 32.02,
      "end": 33.6,
      "text": "They were talking loudly.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他们在大声地说话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 34.5,
      "end": 36.54,
      "text": "I got very angry.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我非常生气。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 37.36,
      "end": 39.62,
      "text": "I could not hear the actors.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我听不见演员在说什么。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 40.58,
      "end": 41.74,
      "text": "I turned round.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我转过身去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 42.58,
      "end": 45.9,
      "text": "I looked at the man and the woman angrily.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我生气地看着那一男一女。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 47.14,
      "end": 49.58,
      "text": "They did not pay any attention.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他们毫不理会。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 50.58,
      "end": 54.2,
      "text": "In the end, I could not bear it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "最后，我忍不住了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 54.76,
      "end": 56.4,
      "text": "I turned round again.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我又转过身去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 57.44,
      "end": 59.94,
      "text": "I can't hear a word.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“我一个字也听不见了！”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 60.72,
      "end": 62.28,
      "text": "I said angrily.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我生气地说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 63.36,
      "end": 65.32,
      "text": "It's none of your business.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“不关你的事。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 66.28,
      "end": 68.34,
      "text": "The young man said rudely.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那青年男子粗鲁地说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 69.18,
      "end": 71.36,
      "text": "This is a private conversation.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "“这是私人谈话！”"
      }
    }
  ]
}
